00:22:44.860 --> 00:22:49.150
that's been happening where these writers
like Jonathan Lethem and Michael Chabon are

00:22:49.150 --> 00:22:54.680
getting a lot of praise for breaking genre
and talking about comics as if they're important,

00:22:54.680 --> 00:22:58.480
but a lot of my friends are second generation
immigrants and so they were like, "You have

00:22:58.480 --> 00:23:03.320
to read this. There's a brown nerd in this
