00:36:46.590 --> 00:36:53.200
it's awesome, but also I still have the energy
to work with young people, which means you

00:36:53.200 --> 00:36:58.450
can put up with a lot of ridicule and being
completely irrelevant to them. And that requires

00:36:58.450 --> 00:37:03.090
a certain kind of constitution and I still
